## Usage

### Maven

> [版本查询](https://search.maven.org/search?q=authz-spring-boot-starter)

```xml

<dependency>
    <groupId>cn.omisheep</groupId>
    <artifactId>authz-spring-boot-starter</artifactId>
    <version>1.2.10</version>
</dependency>
```
